iles**\\n\\nIt seems like the task might be done, but I want to be sure. I’m considering using commands like `mdfind` or `grep` to search effectively. I’m thinking it might help to focus the search on just the `.openclaw` files. I should also check in smaller directories, like `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research` and `.openclaw`, looking for the exact title. This should help narrow things down!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我先定位到了这条告警的模版，再把对应推送关掉。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e706db840e9e5ef0169ead8fdae8881989e0551f19dd4f638\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_oIQIgu9uQmevrEgQfrTjosSw|fc_0e706db840e9e5ef0169ead8fdbb3c81988294d1b782fa54a8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport os\nroots=['/Users/ling/.openclaw','/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace']\npatterns=['持仓止损监控','硬止损告警','软止损预警','风控参数']\nfor root in roots:\n    for dp, dns, fns in os.walk(root):\n        dns[:] = [d for d in dns if d not in {'.git','node_modules','dist','build','coverage','.cache','Library','Caches'}]\n        for fn in fns:\n            path=os.path.join(dp,fn)\n            try:\n                if os.path.getsize(path)>2_000_000:\n                    continue\n                with open(path,'r',encoding='utf-8',errors='ignore') as f:\n                    txt=f.read()\n                if all(p in txt for p in patterns[:2]) or any(p in txt for p in patterns):\n                    if '持仓止损监控' in txt or '硬止损告警' in txt:\n                        print(path)\n            except Exception:\n                pass\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":60,"yieldMs":10000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport os\\nroots=['/Users/ling/.openclaw','/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace']\\npatterns=['持仓止损监控','硬止损告警','软止损预警','风控参数']\\nfor root in roots:\\n    for dp, dns, fns in os.walk(root):\\n        dns[:] = [d for d in dns if d not in {'.git','node_modules','dist','build','coverage','.cache','Library','Caches'}]\\n        for fn in fns:\\n            path=os.path.join(dp,fn)\\n            try:\\n                if os.path.getsize(path)>2_000_000:\\n                    continue\\n                with open(path,'r',encoding='utf-8',errors='ignore') as f:\\n                    txt=f.read()\\n                if all(p in txt for p in patterns[:2]) or any(p in txt for p in patterns):\\n                    if '持仓止损监控' in txt or '硬止损告警' in txt:\\n                        print(path)\\n            except Exception:\\n                pass\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":60,\"yieldMs\":10000}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":48709,"output":372,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49081,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776998645194,"responseId":"resp_0e706db840e9e5ef0169ead8f93500819884f3b18f3ea656a0"}}
